---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro'
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Cookie Policy · CrossFit La Mola"
  description="Cookie policy for the CrossFit La Mola website, Terrassa. Information about the cookies we use, how to manage them and your rights under GDPR regulations."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .legal-content{ max-width:780px; margin:0 auto;}
      .legal-content h2{ font-family:var(--f-display); font-weight:600; font-size:clamp(22px,2.5vw,28px); margin:48px 0 16px; letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
      .legal-content h3{ font-family:var(--f-display); font-weight:500; font-size:18px; margin:32px 0 12px;}
      .legal-content p, .legal-content li{ font-family:var(--f-serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--bone-2); margin:0 0 16px;}
      .legal-content ul{ padding-left:24px; margin:0 0 20px;}
      .legal-content li{ margin-bottom:8px;}
      .legal-content a{ color:var(--accent-hi); text-decoration:underline;}
      .legal-content strong{ color:var(--bone); font-weight:500;}
      .legal-content table{ width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; margin:20px 0 32px; font-family:var(--f-serif); font-size:15px;}
      .legal-content th, .legal-content td{ text-align:left; padding:12px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
      .legal-content th{ font-family:var(--f-mono); font-size:11px; letter-spacing:.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--muted);}
      .legal-content td{ color:var(--bone-2);}
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <Nav />

  <section class="page-hero" style="min-height:40svh">
    <div class="bg" style="background:#1a1814"></div>
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="crumb"><a href="/en">Home</a><span>/</span><span>Cookies</span></div>
      <h1>Cookie<br><em class="serif">policy</em><span class="dot">.</span></h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sec ink">
    <div class="inner legal-content">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> 20 May 2026</p>

      <h2>1. Data controller</h2>
      <p>The data controller for cookie usage on this website is <strong>TERRAWOD FITNESS, S.L.</strong> (trading as CrossFit La Mola), with Spanish VAT <strong>ESB55446280</strong> and registered office at Av. del Vallès 724C, 08227 Terrassa, Barcelona, Spain. Contact email: <a href="mailto:info@crossfitlamola.com">info@crossfitlamola.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>2. What are cookies?</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small text files stored on your device when you visit a website. They allow us to remember your preferences, analyze how you use the site, and improve your browsing experience.</p>

      <h2>3. What cookies do we use?</h2>

      <h3>Technical and preference cookies (necessary)</h3>
      <p>Essential for the website to function and to remember your cookie preferences. They do not require consent under Spanish LSSI-CE art. 22.2.</p>
      <table>
        <tr><th>Name</th><th>Type</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr>
        <tr><td>cookie-consent-v1</td><td>localStorage</td><td>Remembers your choice about analytics cookies</td><td>Persistent (until you delete it)</td></tr>
      </table>

      <h3>Analytics cookies (require consent)</h3>
      <p>These help us understand how visitors use the website to improve it. They are only set if you give explicit consent on the banner.</p>
      <table>
        <tr><th>Name</th><th>Provider</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Duration</th></tr>
        <tr><td>_ga</td><td>Google Analytics</td><td>Distinguish users</td><td>2 years</td></tr>
        <tr><td>_ga_*</td><td>Google Analytics</td><td>Maintain session state</td><td>2 years</td></tr>
      </table>

      <h2>4. Third-party cookies and international transfer</h2>
      <p>If you accept analytics cookies, cookies from <strong>Google Analytics (Google LLC)</strong> will be installed. These cookies may involve the transfer of data to the United States, where Google has servers. Google adheres to the EU-U.S. Data Privacy Framework, which guarantees an adequate level of protection according to the European Commission.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Google Analytics:</strong> Privacy policy: <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">policies.google.com/privacy</a> · Opt-out: <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">browser add-on</a></li>
        <li><strong>Google Maps:</strong> If you view external maps, Google may install its own cookies. <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's policy</a>.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. How to manage cookies?</h2>
      <p>You can accept, reject or configure analytics cookies through the banner that appears when you first visit the website. You can also change your choice at any time from the <strong>"Manage cookies"</strong> link in the footer.</p>
      <p>You can also configure your browser to block or delete cookies:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Chrome</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/cookies-information-websites-store-on-your-computer" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Mozilla Firefox</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Safari</a></li>
        <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/delete-and-manage-cookies-168dab11-0753-043d-7c16-ede5947fc64d" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p>Please note that blocking all cookies may affect the functionality of some parts of the website.</p>

      <h2>6. Updates</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy to reflect changes in the cookies we use or in applicable legislation. We recommend reviewing it periodically. The date of the last update appears at the beginning of the document.</p>

      <h2>7. Contact</h2>
      <p>If you have questions about our cookie policy or want to exercise your rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@crossfitlamola.com">info@crossfitlamola.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
